<head>Adjunct Descriptive Data
</head>
<relatedmaterial encodinganalog="544$a">
<head>Related Material
</head>
<p>For more information about the early days of apartment conversion to condominiums in Arlington, see <extref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://ead.lib.virginia.edu/vivaxtf/view?docId=arlington/ViAr00034.xml"><title render="bold">RG 34, Records of Tenants of Arlington County</title></extref>. <extref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://ead.lib.virginia.edu/vivaxtf/view?docId=arlington/ViAr00325.xml"><title render="bold">RG 325, Brian H. Ford Colonial Village Collection</title></extref> and <extref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://ead.lib.virginia.edu/vivaxtf/view?docId=arlington/ViAr00372.xml"><title render="bold">RG 372, Nnoka Colonial Village Materials</title></extref> have more information on Colonial Village specifically.
</p>
</relatedmaterial>
